= Checkboxes

Checkbox rules create interactive checkbox elements.

== Basic Checkboxes

- [ ] Unchecked checkbox
- [x] Checked checkbox

== Checkboxes in Lists

* [ ] First unchecked item
* [x] Second checked item
* [ ] Third unchecked item

== Checkboxes with Text

- [ ] Task one: Complete the first task
- [x] Task two: This task is done
- [ ] Task three: Still pending

== Checkboxes with Formatting

- [x] Task with *bold* text
- [ ] Task with _italic_ text
- [x] Task with `monospaced` text

== Checkboxes with Links

- [ ] Read the https://example.com[documentation]
- [x] Complete the setup
- [ ] Test the application

== Nested Checkboxes

* [ ] Main task
** [x] Sub-task one
** [ ] Sub-task two
* [x] Another main task

== Checkboxes in Ordered Lists

. [ ] First step
. [x] Second step (completed)
. [ ] Third step

== Checkboxes with Other Content

- [x] Completed task

  Additional details about this task.

- [ ] Pending task

  More information here.


